				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Sionachie’s Crescendo needed for exping groups?<a name="56161"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 11 04 3:12 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Generally the puller isn't grouped with the MT group since there is a pull channel, which the main tanks join.  Most of the time, at least for me, the pullers are chain pulling.  So, being in with the puller means totally shut down on singing, which doesn't fly with me.  Having the puller in another group allows for free singing, with the exclusion of aoe songs.
<br />

<br />
Being aware of puller proximity is a skill bards have to learn.  However, with better group setup the amount of awareness can be greatly reduced, only affecting aoe songs compared to all songs.
<br />

<br />
Polara Magami</span></td>
